Class GenericPatternGroup

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IQueryGroup

    public class GenericPatternGroup
extends BasePatternGroup
    Generic implementation of IQueryGroup, covering an arbitrarily chosen set of patterns. Use the public constructor or static GenericPatternGroup.of(...) methods to instantiate.
    Author:
    Mark Czotter
